com.twcable.grabbit.tools.util

Interface Either<L,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - the type of Left
    R - the type of Right
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Either.Left, Either.Right

    public interface Either<L,R>
extends java.util.function.Supplier<R>

    An either/or (XOR) value represented as Left/Right.

    By convention, Left is an error value whereas Right is a success value.
